item.title: CVE-2019-5490|2024-08-04T19:54:53.575Z -- netapp%2C%20inc. -- netapp%20service%20processor
item.description: Certain versions between 2.x to 5.x (refer to advisory) of the NetApp Service Processor firmware were shipped with a default account enabled that could allow unauthorized arbitrary command execution. Any platform listed in the advisory Impact section may be affected and should be upgraded to a fixed version of Service Processor firmware IMMEDIATELY.
